Package: dbxml-doc
Architecture: all
Description: Oracle Berkeley DB XML Documentation [html]
 This package contains documentation in HTML format for all of
 the APIs (C, C++, C#, STL, Java, Tcl, Perl) and utilities provided by Oracle
 Berkeley DB XML.

Package: dbxml-util
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Oracle Berkeley DB XML Utilities
 This package provides different tools for manipulating databases in the Oracle
 Berkeley DB XML database format.

Package: libdbxml
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Priority: standard
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Suggests: dbxml-util
Description: Oracle Berkeley DB XML Libraries [runtime]
 This is the runtime package for programs that use the v2.5 Berkeley
 library.

Package: libdbxml-dbg
Architecture: any
Section: debug
Priority: extra
Depends: libdbxml (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Oracle Berkeley DB XML Libraries [debug]
 This package provides the debug symbols for the Oracle Berkeley DB XML
 library.

Package: libdbxml-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Priority: extra
Depends: libdbxml (= ${binary:Version})
Suggests: dbxml-doc
Description: Oracle Berkeley DB XML Libraries [development]
 This is the development package which contains headers and static
 libraries for the Oracle Berkeley DB XML library.

Package: libdbxml-java
Architecture: any
