Package: libdbxml-java-gcj
Architecture: any
Section: java
Priority: optional
Depends: libdbxml-java (>= ${source:Version}), libgcj-common (>> 1:4.1.1-13), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Oracle Berkeley DB XML Libraries for Java (native code)
 This package provides the Java interface for the Oracle Berkeley DB XML
 library.
 .
 This package contains the natively compiled code for use by gij.

Package: libdbxml-tcl
Architecture: any
Section: interpreters
Priority: extra
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Oracle Berkeley DB XML Libraries for Tcl [module]
 This package provides a Tcl module suitable for accessing Oracle Berkeley DB XML
 databases from within Tcl programs.

